    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "严震直",
        "二差役",
        "四青袍",
        "天理昭彰循环报",
        "建文帝",
        "这是你自作自受大限到"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（建文帝上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "乾坤混乱干戈动，\n何日才得定太平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我、建文帝。自从逃出皇城，君臣暂在白云观隐身，观院却还僻静，倒也清闲。\n今日忽然眼跳心惊，不知主何先兆，令人好难解也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "为什么心惊肉又跳？\n行不安来坐不牢。\n吉凶祸福难猜着。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水底鱼〗。四青袍、二差役、严震直同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四青袍、二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是白云观。"
        },
        {
          "character": "严震直",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "打了进去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四青袍、二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍、二差役同打门，同进。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "严震直",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哈哈哈……你在这里？"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！你们是些什么人？为何打进我的观来？"
        },
        {
          "character": "严震直",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀呀呸！事到如今，还想隐瞒，难道我不认得你是建文帝么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你认得我是建文帝，难道我就不认得你是严震直么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "严震直",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日才认得你严老爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好奸贼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "建文帝",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "你平白无故起波涛，\n苦害忠良为哪条？\n难逃骂名万古标！"
        },
        {
          "character": "天理昭彰循环报、严震直",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呸！"
        },
        {
          "character": "天理昭彰循环报、严震直",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "今奉旨意出皇朝，\n海角天涯捕亡逃。\n却又何必絮叨叨？"
        },
        {
          "character": "天理昭彰循环报、严震直",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来呀！铁链手扭打上囚牢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "这是你自作自受大限到、四青袍、二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍同与建文帝带手铐，车夫上，搀建文帝上车，众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "建文帝→二差役",
          "turns": 1
        },
        {
          "edge": "二差役→严震直",
