    {
      "scene_index": 3,
      "label": "第三场",
      "characters_present": [
        "程济"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "无量佛！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程济上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "昨奉师命送故交，\n一路凄凉落叶飘。\n朝东暮西奔波劳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "程济。昨奉师命，护送故交，畅谈彻夜。今朝洒泪而别。想大师定在观中悬望。\n不免急急赶回便了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "回复师命忙就道，\n怕的是大师愁闷心焦。\n为何此时身发躁？\n遍体生津似水浇。\n猛抬头见面前岔事一条。"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！这山门被毁，隔扇打坏，是何缘故？也罢！不免请出大师一问，便知端的。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程济向内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请大师！有请大师！有请大师！\n啊，大师不见，想是在观外游玩，待我寻找。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程济出门。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊大师，啊大师！哎呀，好奇怪也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "四平调",
          "musical_style": "四平调",
          "style_family": "四平调",
          "text": "为什么叫不应来寻不着，\n难道说这半山出了妖魔？\n大师踪迹难捉摸。\n费思索解不出其故为何。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四青袍 （内同白） 嗯咳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀！那厢来了一伙人役，待我闪在一旁，听他们讲些什么。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要知心腹事，但听口中言。"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
        "line_counts": {
