    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "二差役",
        "差役乙",
        "差役甲"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍、二差役同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二差役",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奉了严爷命，捉拿建文君。来在中途路，想起老道人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我奉了严尚书之命，捉拿建文皇帝。皇帝拿获了，中途路上，严爷又想起什\n么老道程济来啦，又命你我二次捉拿。咱们观中走走！"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "走喳！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四青袍、二差役同走圆场。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来此已是。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二差役同向内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老道程济！老道程济！\n这边不见，那边寻找。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二差役同向内。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "二差役",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老道程济！老道程济！"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四下不见，难道叫你我变一个不成吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役乙",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我先去回复严爷！"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "言之有理。请！"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役甲",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回复严命，不见道人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "差役乙",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四下无有，哪里找寻！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "二差役→差役甲",
