    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "程济"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程济上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀，愧煞我也！适才听差役言道，建文帝被他们拿住；中途路上，又想起我\n程济，故此前来捉拿。想我对天发下誓愿：永保大师无事；今日被他们拿去，\n有何脸面去见去世的先帝也！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "二黄导板",
          "musical_style": "二黄导板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "料不想平地风波祸事到，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（回龙） 莫非是天绝人定数难逃？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "好容易死中求活把君保，\n十六载的功劳一旦抛。\n枉在人间逞英豪？"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "跟踪差役——"
        },
        {
          "character": "程济",
          "line_type": "二黄散板",
          "musical_style": "二黄散板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "踉跄就道，\n要救大师出笼牢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（程济下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
